        If you draw and animate with CSS, make music in the browser, play with typography, or do anything else really: please submit a proposal.
      </p>
      {{ callForArtistsButton(
        'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd3vGFs8_0_pcMAYEUq8uP3-reyzPMVJwBXSpkjbct9svrBkg/viewform',
        truncateOnMobile = true,
        openNewTab = false,
        centered = false
      ) }}
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="c-content c-content--salmon">
    <div class="l-container">
      <h2 class="fz--beta">
        Become a Sponsor!
      </h2>
      <p class="copy">
